OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of UK children growing up in
OL,6, "very deep poverty" has risen to 1.8   
OL,7, million, a leading charity has warned. 
OL,9,FThe Joseph Rowntree Foundation (JRF)   
OL,10,Fsaid the figure had increased by       
OL,11,F500,000 since 2012 and soaring energy  
OL,12,Fprices rises could hit more families.  
OL,14,FRebecca, from West Yorkshire, said it  
OL,15,Fwas "degrading" that her children woke 
OL,16,Fup "shivering" as she couldn't afford  
OL,17,Fto leave the heating on.               
OL,19,FThe government said it had taken       
OL,20,Fdecisive steps to support families.    
